description.en: This REC module covers equipment that can be mounted in a building, e.g., HVAC systems, electrical systems, plumbing, alarms, computer networks, etc.

comment.en: Equipment that is permanently or semi-permanently mounted or installed in a building, e.g., HVAC systems, electrical systems, elevators, CC-TV-systems, etc.
Imperial measure for the recovery rate of a boiler (gallons per hour).
